id=apex-hide-daemon
name=APEX Hide Daemon
version=v1.0
versionCode=1
author=APEX-Root Team
description=Standalone root daemon for transparent root hiding. Runs at boot via Magisk/KSU/APatch service.d, provides mount-namespace isolation + LD_PRELOAD libc interception for target apps. Independent of the APEX-Root app — works even when app is not running. Communicates with app via Unix socket at /dev/socket/apex_hide.sock.
